#### Description

This dashboard provides visibility into DNS response activity. It summarizes key metrics such as authority answer counts and categorizes DNS events by Class, Type, Flag, Transport protocol, and Application protocol to support quick identification of unusual patterns.


**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/infoblox_threat_defense/overview)**
